data.description: Welcome home to this open, airy &, well-maintained home located in a prime Marietta location. Perfectly situated on a corner lot - as you stroll down your private sidewalk lined with azaleas - you will be surprised once you step into the entry by the soaring two story great room and a bright open concept Kitchen, Dining and Living areas, cozy fireplace - lots of windows and light. This home has so much to offer and has been updated with genuine engineered hardwood flooring throughout, updated tiled bathrooms and kitchen. This home has NO carpet. The primary bedroom on the main level is spacious and features an ensuite bathroom with double vanities, separate shower and soaking tub and walk in closet. The laundry area and powder room are also on the main level. There is a large one car garage that has additional space for hobbies and/or storage. Upstairs you have two generously sized bedrooms and full bathroom. All neutral colors throughout the home -so you can decorate your style to suit your needs. Outdoors is perfect for entertaining with a wraparound large patio BBQ ready, or space for gardening. There is also a barn for storage, hobbies or that special outdoor space you have been waiting for. The backyard is fenced in and offers privacy. For owner occupants - if you have been looking for an assumable loan - there is one available for those who want to pay the equity and can qualify for the super low VA rates from 2021. This home is located so close to major highways, hospitals, shopping, restaurants, parks, malls. Move -in ready and all we need is you!
